19labah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOn the middle night of Sha'ban, Allah looks down upon His creation and He forgives the believers, gives respite to the unbelievers, and He abandons the people of malice to their malice until they give it up.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38897,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/23\/connect-ramadan-shaban\/","url_meta":{"origin":32203,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sha\u2019ban: The Prophet connects fasting Ramadan and Sha\u2019ban","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The most beloved month to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, for fasting was Sha\u2019ban, then he would connect it with Ramadan. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2431 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064f\u0651\u0647\u064f\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/prophet-connects-shaban-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":32203,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sha\u2019ban: The Prophet fasts in Sha\u2019ban before Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would fast until we said he will never break his fast, and he would not fast until we said he would never fast. I did not see the Prophet complete an entire month of fasting except for Ramadan,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27659,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/16\/sawm-shaban-ramadan-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":32203,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: The Prophet fasts Sha\u2019ban and Ramadan together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: I did not see the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, fast for two consecutive months in a row except for Sha\u2019ban and Ramadan. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 736 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0635\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/ramadan-make-up-missed-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":32203,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Making up missed fasts throughout the year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cI had to make up some fasts I missed during the month of Ramadan, but I was unable to do so until the month of Sha\u2019ban as\u00a0I was busy with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32203","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=32203"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32203\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=32203"}],"wp:term"